keivan de-is'mar mishmeih de-Shmuel. We don't like to say there are competing

1097
00:53:39,390 --> 00:53:42,990
traditions. So כיון דאיתמר משמיה דשמואל בהדיא, keivan de-is'mar mishmeih de-Shmuel ba-hadya,

1098
00:53:43,070 --> 00:53:45,790
since we have an explicit ruling in the name of שמואל Shmuel

1099
00:53:45,790 --> 00:53:49,360
that יש זיקה, yeish zika, so ומשמיה דרב כתרי אמוראי. u-mishmeih de-Rav

1100
00:53:49,360 --> 00:53:53,410
ke-trei amora'ei. An alternate to that we could say it's a debate

1101
00:53:53,790 --> 00:53:55,630
either it's a debate of רב Rav and שמואל Shmuel or it's

1102
00:53:55,630 --> 00:53:58,590
a debate of what רב Rav two versions of what רב Rav

1103
00:53:58,590 --> 00:54:01,310
said. So לא שבקינן משמיה דשמואל בהדיא. lo shavkinan mishmeih de-Shmuel ba-hadya.

1104
00:54:01,370 --> 00:54:03,890
We don't abandon the position of saying that רב יהודה Rav Yehuda

1105
00:54:03,890 --> 00:54:06,390
got it from שמואל Shmuel who we know that that's שמואל's Shmuel

1106
00:54:06,390 --> 00:54:08,884
position. So it's a debate of רב Rav and שמואל Shmuel ומוקמינן

1107
00:54:08,884 --> 00:54:11,990
כתרי אמוראי אליבא דרב. ve-mokeiminan ke-trei amora'ei aliba de-Rav. We don't abandon

1108
00:54:11,990 --> 00:54:14,490
that to say that there's a debate about what רב Rav actually

1109
00:54:14,490 --> 00:54:18,750
said. Debates between different אמוראים Amoraim we know, but we'd rather that

1110
00:54:18,750 --> 00:54:21,810
that be than an actual sort of you know corruption of the

1111
00:54:21,810 --> 00:54:26,110
tradition or a loss of the tradition which is a debate of

1112
00:54:26,110 --> 00:54:28,590
what רב Rav actually said. So we have the two statements whether

1113
00:54:28,590 --> 00:54:31,190
you can or can't marry the mother. It could have been two

1114
00:54:31,190 --> 00:54:34,130
versions of what רב Rav says. We're saying it's a debate between

1115
00:54:34,130 --> 00:54:36,050
רב Rav and שמואל. Shmuel. רב Rav says you can marry the

1116
00:54:36,050 --> 00:54:38,290
mother. שמואל Shmuel says you can't. שמואל Shmuel says יש זיקה yeish

1117
00:54:38,290 --> 00:54:41,450
zika and that's why you tell לוי Levi wait to consummate your

1118
00:54:41,450 --> 00:54:44,830
marriage with לאה Leah until we get רחל Rachel sort of dealt

1119
00:54:44,830 --> 00:54:47,230
with. Okay, and now we'll just wrap

1120
00:54:47,230 --> 00:54:50,150
this up, just do one more minute to get to the משנה.

1121
00:54:49,970 --> 00:54:51,350
Mishnah. Okay. אמר רב כהנא, Amar Rav Kahana, אמריתי לשמעתא Amrisi Lishmaysta

1122
00:54:51,350 --> 00:54:52,410
קמיה דרב זביד Kamei D'Rav Zvid מנהרדעא, Min Nahardea, I told over

1123
00:54:52,410 --> 00:54:53,970
this discussion in front of רב זביד Rav Zvid from נהרדעא. Nahardea.

1124
00:54:53,970 --> 00:54:54,230
אמר, Amar, he

1125
00:54:58,910 --> 00:55:01,730
said, אתון הכי מתניתו לה, Atun Hachi Masnisu Lah, that's how

1126
00:55:05,730 --> 00:55:06,930
you tell over this

1127
00:55:08,630 --> 00:55:09,330
discussion. אנן בהדיא

1128
00:55:11,730 --> 00:55:12,410
מתניתו לה, Anan Behedya Masnisu Lah, you

1129
00:55:15,230 --> 00:55:17,160
mean you said that there was a question whether רב יהודה Rav

1130
00:55:17,160 --> 00:55:19,030
Yehuda was saying it in the name of רב Rav or שמואל.

1131
00:55:18,730 --> 00:55:22,610
Shmuel. We have an explicit version that רב יהודה Rav Yehuda explicitly

1132
00:55:22,610 --> 00:55:25,510
said it in the name of שמואל. Shmuel. אמר רב יהודה אמר

1133
00:55:25,510 --> 00:55:26,098
שמואל, Amar Rav Yehuda Amar Shmuel, שומרת יבם שמתה אסור באמה, Shomeres

1134
00:55:26,098 --> 00:55:28,850
Yavam Shemesa Asur B'imah, that if she died you can't marry the

1135
00:55:29,630 --> 00:55:32,090
mother. אלמא קסבר יש זיקה, Alma Kasavar Yesh Zika, he holds יש

1136
00:55:32,090 --> 00:55:33,550
זיקה. Yesh Zika. ואזדא שמואל לטעמיה, V'asra Shmuel L'taimei, and he's consistent,

1137
00:55:33,550 --> 00:55:36,610
שמואל Shmuel with another position we know, another statement he knows he

1138
00:55:36,610 --> 00:55:39,410
says that says יש זיקה, Yesh Zika, דאמר שמואל הלכה כרב יהודה

1139
00:55:39,410 --> 00:55:40,290
בן בתירה. D'amar Shmuel Halacha K'Rav Yehuda Ben Beseira. We rule like

1140
00:55:40,490 --> 00:55:42,190
רב יהודה בן בתירה Rav Yehuda Ben Beseira that we tell לוי

1141
00:55:41,850 --> 00:55:46,290
Levi don't consummate it with לאה Leah until until your brother deals

1142
00:55:46,290 --> 00:55:49,130
with רחל. Rachel. וצריכי, V'tzrichi, and שמואל Shmuel had to say both

1143
00:55:50,190 --> 00:55:52,410
positions. אי אשמעינן יש זיקה, Ei Ashmeinan Yesh Zika, if he had

1144
00:55:52,410 --> 00:55:55,890
said יש זיקה Yesh Zika in the case of when she dies

1145
00:55:55,890 --> 00:55:56,970
and not marry the

1146
00:55:58,330 --> 00:56:00,570
mother, הני מילי בחד, Hani Mili B'chad, that's because there's only one

1147
00:56:00,570 --> 00:56:03,670
person around, so it's that's why don't marry the mother because there's

1148
00:56:03,670 --> 00:56:06,330
a real זיקה. Zika. אבל בתרי, Aval B'trei, in the case of

1149
00:56:06,330 --> 00:56:08,810
שמעון Shimon and לוי, Levi, לא, Lo, maybe it wouldn't be a

1150
00:56:08,810 --> 00:56:11,470
problem because maybe the זיקה Zika is with שמעון Shimon and let

1151
00:56:11,470 --> 00:56:14,767
לוי Levi consummate his marriage. קא משמע לן, Kamashma Lan, so it's

1152
00:56:14,767 --> 00:56:16,290
telling you we rule even in the שמעון Shimon and לוי Levi

1153
00:56:16,290 --> 00:56:19,630
case, don't consummate the marriage, there's זיקה Zika even when there are

1154
00:56:19,630 --> 00:56:20,070
two brothers

1155
00:56:21,870 --> 00:56:22,679
around. ואי אשמעינן הלכה כרב יהודה בן בתירה, V'ei Ashmeinan Halacha K'Rav

1156
00:56:22,679 --> 00:56:24,530
Yehuda Ben Beseira, had we just said that

1157
00:56:25,990 --> 00:56:28,230
פסק, Psak, so הני מילי בחיים, Hani Mili B'chaim, fine, there there's

1158
00:56:28,230 --> 00:56:32,090
זיקה Zika because רחל Rachel is still alive, so there's a live

1159
00:56:32,090 --> 00:56:36,310
זיקה, Zika, so therefore don't consummate the marriage with לאה. Leah. אבל

1160
00:56:36,310 --> 00:56:39,510
אחר מיתה, Aval Achar Misa, if the woman's dead and then פקע

1161
00:56:39,510 --> 00:56:41,430
ליה זיקה, Paka Lay Zika, then I would say there's no זיקה,

1162
00:56:41,110 --> 00:56:42,724
Zika, marry the mother. קא משמע לן דזיקה בכדי לא פקע, Kamashma

1163
00:56:42,724 --> 00:56:45,687
Lan D'zika Bichdi Lo Paka, זיקה Zika doesn't go away by itself.

1164
00:56:45,687 --> 00:56:48,030
So in the end we conclude, and this seems to be the

1165
00:56:48,910 --> 00:56:51,370
position of the גמרא, Gemara, that we say יש זיקה Yesh Zika

1166
00:56:51,370 --> 00:56:55,110
even in the most extreme cases. Meaning even after the woman has

1167
00:56:55,110 --> 00:56:58,450
died, זיקה Zika is still around, and even if there's multiple brothers

1168
00:56:59,110 --> 00:57:00,790
and only one of them is going to do יבום Yibum or

1169
00:57:00,790 --> 00:57:02,990
חליצה, Chalitzah, we still say there's זיקה Zika with all of the

1170
00:57:04,670 --> 00:57:05,470
brothers. Okay. Phew.
